original_title: AAA: Lucha Libre World Cup - Guadalajara, MX
overview: On March 19th Lucha Libre World Cup: Guadalajara, MX 2023 is live! The event features the 2023 Lucha Libre World Cup Women's Tournament and 2023 Lucha Libre World Cup Men's Tournament. The first round matches for both women's and men's tournaments are already announced and you can check them below:  2023 Lucha Libre World Cup Women's Tournament First Round Matches  Team Mexico vs. Team Japan, Team United States vs. Team Rest of The World  2023 Lucha Libre World Cup Men's Tournament First Round Matches  Team Canada vs. Team Europe, Team United States vs. Team Japan, Team Mexico vs. Team Rest of The World, Dream Team vs. Team Latin America
title: AAA: Lucha Libre World Cup - Guadalajara, MX
